name: b+w figure study 01 by artist flowmada_art
description:
Greetings fellow crypto-artists+collectors! I'm pretty new to this whole NFT/digital art thing but I'm learning a lot as I go. I'm excited to share some of my artwork with the creative hivemind. I'm a 29 y.o. self taught artist who primarily works with traditional media. But plague times have made me bored and eager to try new things e.g. learn to use Procreate.

Here's one of several in a series of monochromatic figure/portrait drawings done while figuring out how to use Procreate. 

2048x2048 pixels
22,612 strokes made
10 hrs 32 min work time
Reference photo used for nude model.
